channel.title: [Question] Recommend a base for a big project
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape community!
I am planning to work on a big RSPS project, and was wondering what base would be best to work with.
I'm looking for a fairly newer runescape version base.
Feedback with me appreciated!
Thanks.
